title: Judy Greer
description:
Actress Judy Greer feels very privileged to be Conan O’Brien’s friend.


 

Judy sits down with Conan to discuss being late bloomers, onscreen intimacy with George Clooney, Judy's new scripted podcast ‘Self Center’, and trying to eat more candy. Plus, Conan bemoans the struggle of shopping for compression socks.

 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.

 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
author: conaf@teamcoco.com (Team Coco & Earwolf)
